        <h1>Hi, I am Ryen Wu.</h1>

        <p class="intro">
          I work on leaf spectral trait inversion, physics-informed neural networks,
          and embedded vision systems.
        </p>

        <div class="buttons">
          <a href="/projects">View Projects</a>
          <a href="/research">Research</a>
          <a href="/cv.pdf">Download CV</a>
