      <section>
        <h2>Featured Research</h2>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Leaf Spectral Trait Inversion</h3>
          <p>
            A physics-informed learning framework for estimating leaf traits such as
            Cab, Car, Cw, Prot, and CBC from spectral data using PROSPECT-PRO.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Attention-based Spectral Encoder</h3>
          <p>
            Exploring CNN, self-attention, VAE, and branch-wise encoder structures
            for VIS-NIR-SWIR spectral representation learning.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Engineering Projects</h2>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>YOLOv8 on RK3588</h3>
          <p>
            Real-time object detection and segmentation pipeline using YOLOv8,
            RKNN, ROS, and embedded camera streaming.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
